	(396,1,'2016-04-04 16:39:26','2016-04-04 16:39:26','<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Something Legendary is coming to the Sanford Center November 12th, 2016!</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-442\" src=\"http://gigazonegaming.local/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/diamonds-lol.png\" alt=\"diamonds-lol\" width=\"878\" height=\"365\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Summoners! Grab your teammates, don your favorite skin, and come compete in Paul Bunyan Communication\'s first League of Legends Tournament! Boasting over $4,500 in cash and prizes for competitors, as well as door prize drawings for attendees, you’ll want to be sure to be there for all of the excitement!</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Please register your email address below and we’ll keep you up to date on the latest news and updates regarding the tournament, team sign-up process, and further details as they materialize from the rift! <sup><i class=\"fa fa-asterisk\"></i></sup></p>\r\n\r\n[update-sign-up]\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\" class=\"disclaimer\"><sup><i class=\"fa fa-asterisk\"></i></sup> Tournament only open to participation by residents in the 218 area code and must be at least 13 years of age or older.</p>\n\r[gigazone-info]','Home','','publish','closed','closed','','home','','','2016-04-21 16:03:58','2016-04-21 16:03:58','',0,'http://gigazonegaming.local/?page_id=396',0,'page','',0),
